faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nUSS Carl Vinson wasn't headed for North Korea when defense officials said it was<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cnbc.com/2017/04/18/uss-carl-vinson-wasnt-headed-for-north-korea-when-defense-officials-said-it-was.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2Fuss-carl-vinson-wasnt-headed-for-north-korea-when-defense-officials-said-it-was.html&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0Fy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=17e7db41\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cnbc.com/2017/04/18/uss-carl-vinson-wasnt-headed-for-north-korea-when-defense-officials-said-it-was.html</a>"}]}